name: BrandBucket
tag_list: brand, domain, logo, rebrand, design, marketing
overview:
BrandBucket creates pre-packaged brands, including the logo and a dot com domain name, for great new products and services to adopt. Brandbucket caters to entrepreneurs, startups, creatives and small businesses. We have a vast list of branded domain names and great informative blogs relating to naming your business, product, or service.

We are very particular about the brands we develop. We look for unique memorable names that can become the future Googles and Yahoos, and at the same time we are very much particular about the aesthetic and the brand feel of our names. You can think of us as the supplier of great brands-to-be. Please check out our website at http://www.brandbucket.com.
